  "body": "<p>I am <em>so</em> thrilled to be sharing <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2012/07/amy-tangerine-ready-set-go-reveal.html\">Ready Set Go</a> with you today! It's my third line with American Crafts, but a slight departure from the others since it's my first Autumn-inspired line. I am in love with the fresh color palette and the eclectic mix of icons - I hope you enjoy it as much as I do! It should begin to hit stores in late August.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"10a-6a00d8357de06869e20176163172bd970c-600x98.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732049642-ECCYP1T4SVVG72K40OJF/10a-6a00d8357de06869e20176163172bd970c-600x98.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"10b-6a00d8357de06869e20167683c6c1a970b-600x399.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732051058-WNDHUGZEOIGW2QP7HYXT/10b-6a00d8357de06869e20167683c6c1a970b-600x399.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10c-6a00d8357de06869e20167683c6cba970b-600x399.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732052397-OBPWTRNCVWFF4PTDQ6OQ/10c-6a00d8357de06869e20167683c6cba970b-600x399.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10d-6a00d8357de06869e20167683c6d35970b-600x399.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732052489-Z7F36LJLV0PSWN5GKJ5B/10d-6a00d8357de06869e20167683c6d35970b-600x399.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10e-6a00d8357de06869e201774317863c970d-600x399.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732134273-0QFEH5SEU3SQKJXOXGC0/10e-6a00d8357de06869e201774317863c970d-600x399.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10f-6a00d8357de06869e201774317de9a970d.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732135796-2G880F8ZUD3V1WEU9SUI/10f-6a00d8357de06869e201774317de9a970d.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10g-6a00d8357de06869e201761631d90f970c-500wi1.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732135650-BGSI1M63HOUC2DH0VMPH/10g-6a00d8357de06869e201761631d90f970c-500wi1.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10h-6a00d8357de06869e201774317df4e970d.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732059099-RV0THVEKD5EU6QOKP2LI/10h-6a00d8357de06869e201774317df4e970d.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10i-6a00d8357de06869e201761631d9b7970c-1.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732059242-S9NH1C6O71Y924KWP1UC/10i-6a00d8357de06869e201761631d9b7970c-1.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10k-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cc7fc970b-600x250.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732184816-INWXEL70SSCSICSCF6CP/10k-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cc7fc970b-600x250.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10l-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cfd33970b-600x289.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732184887-5KM63HO6GEYXD6DNM2BJ/10l-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cfd33970b-600x289.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10m-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cfc9f970b-600x251.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732185315-93H0NZKLWEJ71HWENXXM/10m-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cfc9f970b-600x251.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10j-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cc7b0970b.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732060470-4JQT9LLKNI58A7OBCI5F/10j-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cc7b0970b.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10n-6a00d8357de06869e201774318156d970d-600x237.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732063065-TF1VGLRIUOLH4NZEEM5C/10n-6a00d8357de06869e201774318156d970d-600x237.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"10o-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cfe3f970b-600x153.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600732214324-2VL04L5GG5GTBB6BBZHC/10o-6a00d8357de06869e20167683cfe3f970b-600x153.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Loved reading all the comments on the <a href=\"http://americancrafts.typepad.com/studio/2012/07/amy-tangerine-ready-set-go-reveal.html\">American Crafts blog</a>! Just a heads up that you may want to follow me on <a href=\"http://ink361.com/#/users/1718485/photos\">Instagram</a>, if you aren't already. I'll be at CHA next week posting photos and little giveaways. Because we adore you all so much, the goodies up for grabs will include an item only available for those attending the show (except for the ones I will be hiding to give away, of course).</p>"
}